FIRST INTERNET MONEY!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\\n\\n!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\\n\\n!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! https://t.co/CNtUeBdPf2 https://t.co/QRroGyuUC8\",\n      \"created_at\":\"2026-05-01T13:16:45.000Z\",\n      \"author_id\":\"2866424109\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2050202766186807356\"\n      ],\n      \"id\":\"2050202766186807356\",\n      \"public_metrics\":{\n        \"retweet_count\":60,\n        \"reply_count\":549,\n        \"like_count\":3768,\n        \"quote_count\":18,\n        \"bookmark_count\":526,\n        \"impression_count\":554422\n      },\n      \"entities\":{\n        \"urls\":[\n          {\n            \"start\":278,\n            \"end\":301,\n            \"url\":\"https://t.co/CNtUeBdPf2\",\n            \"expanded_url\":\"https://x.com/picoito/status/2050202766186807356/photo/1\",\n            \"display_url\":\"pic.x.com/CNtUeBdPf2\",\n            \"media_key\":\"3_2050202586548953089\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"start\":302,\n            \"end\":325,\n            \"url\":\"https://t.co/QRroGyuUC8\",\n            \"expanded_url\":\"https://twitter.com/picoito/status/2050176963868791075\",\n            \"display_url\":\"x.com/picoito/status…\"\n          }\n        ]\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"text\":\"I tested Pika Agent today…\\n\\nAnd yeah it’s insane.\\n\\nTold it what I wanted, and it helped me create a full project like a real human collaborator.\\n\\nAI creation just became effortless. https://t.co/w4OUtdz1zr https://t.co/29fe20S1FY\",\n      \"created_at\":\"2026-05-01T09:51:32.000Z\",\n      \"author_id\":\"1880958681887485952\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2050151122435002672\"\n      ],\n      \"id\":\"2050151122435002672\",\n      \"public_metrics\":{\n        \"retweet_count\":4,\n        \"reply_count\":9,\n        \"like_count\":61,\n        \"quote_count\":0,\n        \"bookmark_count\":31,\n        \"impression_count\":6585\n      },\n      \"entities\":{\n        \"urls\":[\n          {\n            \"start\":182,\n            \"end\":205,\n            \"url\":\"https://t.co/w4OUtdz1zr\",\n            \"expanded_url\":\"https://x.com/oggii_0/status/2050151122435002672/video/1\",\n            \"display_url\":\"pic.x.com/w4OUtdz1zr\",\n            \"media_key\":\"7_2050151070702424064\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"start\":206,\n            \"end\":229,\n            \"url\":\"https://t.co/29fe20S1FY\",\n            \"expanded_url\":\"https://twitter.com/pika_labs/status/2049196222825779287\",\n            \"display_url\":\"x.com/pika_labs/stat…\"\n          }\n        ]\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"text\":\"OpenClaw 现在可以抓取任何网站而不被屏蔽——零机器人检测，原生绕过 Cloudflare，比 BeautifulSoup 快 774 倍。\\n\\n无需维护选择器。无需变通方案。只需数据。\\n\\n这是不公平的优势，而且完全开源。\\nhttps://t.co/4r4Jg23jal https://t.co/tB8GcY7zjC\",\n      \"created_at\":\"2026-05-01T10:20:02.000Z\",\n      \"author_id\":\"855303666722525184\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2050158295911137370\"\n      ],\n      \"id\":\"2050158295911137370\",\n      \"public_metrics\":{\n        \"retweet_count\":532,\n        \"reply_count\":103,\n        \"like_count\":3313,\n        \"quote_count\":16,\n        \"bookmark_count\":5444,\n        \"impression_count\":226779\n      },\n      \"entities\":{\n        \"urls\":[\n          {\n            \"start\":114,\n            \"end\":137,\n            \"url\":\"https://t.co/4r4Jg23jal\",\n            \"expanded_url\":\"https://github.com/D4Vinci/Scrapling\",\n            \"display_url\":\"github.com/D4Vinci/Scrapl…\",\n            \"images\":[\n              {\n                \"url\":\"https://pbs.twimg.com/news_img/2050158349094993921/vZoPz35J?format=jpg\\u0026name=orig\",\n                \"width\":1344,\n                \"height\":768\n              },\n              {\n                \"url\":\"https://pbs.twimg.com/news_img/2050158349094993921/vZoPz35J?format=jpg\\u0026name=150x150\",\n                \"width\":150,\n                \"height\":150\n              }\n            ],\n            \"status\":200,\n            \"title\":\"GitHub - D4Vinci/Scrapling: \\uD83D\\uDD77️ An adaptive Web Scraping framework that handles everything from a single request to a full-scale crawl!\",\n            \"description\":\"\\uD83D\\uDD77️ An adaptive Web Scraping framework that handles everything from a single request to a full-scale crawl! - D4Vinci/Scrapling\",\n            \"unwound_url\":\"https://github.com/D4Vinci/Scrapling\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"start\":138,\n            \"end\":161,\n            \"url\":\"https://t.co/tB8GcY7zjC\",\n            \"expanded_url\":\"https://x.com/wanerfu/status/2050158295911137370/photo/1\",\n            \"display_url\":\"pic.x.com/tB8GcY7zjC\",\n            \"media_key\":\"3_2050158287375704064\"\n          }\n        ]\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"text\":\"Apple spent 7 years and $3,500 per unit building Vision Pro, this guy did something better with a webcam in his bedroom.\\n\\nAnd no, this isn't a render, it's running live on his laptop right now with a webcam pointed at his hands.\\n\\nThe webcam tracks 21 points on each of his hands https://t.co/UyXVHB8WpI https://t.co/pFJyJTseaC\",\n      \"created_at\":\"2026-05-01T17:09:29.000Z\",\n      \"author_id\":\"1663262095868084228\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2050261337906016505\"\n      ],\n      \"id\":\"2050261337906016505\",\n      \"public_metrics\":{\n        \"retweet_count\":182,\n        \"reply_count\":81,\n        \"like_count\":3066,\n        \"quote_count\":10,\n        \"bookmark_count\":2962,\n        \"impression_count\":2912114\n      },\n      \"entities\":{\n        \"urls\":[\n          {\n            \"start\":279,\n            \"end\":302,\n            \"url\":\"https://t.co/UyXVHB8WpI\",\n            \"expanded_url\":\"https://x.com/defileo/status/2050261337906016505/video/1\",\n            \"display_url\":\"pic.x.com/UyXVHB8WpI\",\n            \"media_key\":\"13_2050261285749788673\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"start\":303,\n            \"end\":326,\n            \"url\":\"https://t.co/pFJyJTseaC\",\n            \"expanded_url\":\"https://twitter.com/1663262095868084228/status/2049509658797224042\",\n            \"display_url\":\"x.com/16632620958680…\"\n          }\n        ]\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"text\":\"A 14 year old in America quit his weekend shifts at Domino's after he realized he could make more money during one lunch break with a laptop than an entire weekend making pizzas for $8.50 an hour.\\n\\nHe was sitting in a coffee shop googling roofing companies near his house for a https://t.co/fOf4iebfED\",\n      \"created_at\":\"2026-05-01T00:38:14.000Z\",\n      \"author_id\":\"1975132988884004864\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2050011880886784235\"\n      ],\n      \"id\":\"2050011880886784235\",\n      \"public_metrics\":{\n        \"retweet_count\":443,\n        \"reply_count\":70,\n        \"like_count\":3799,\n        \"quote_count\":16,\n        \"bookmark_count\":5828,\n        \"impression_count\":966595\n      },\n      \"entities\":{\n        \"urls\":[\n          {\n            \"start\":278,\n            \"end\":301,\n            \"url\":\"https://t.co/fOf4iebfED\",\n            \"expanded_url\":\"https://x.com/marlowxbt/status/2050011880886784235/video/1\",\n            \"display_url\":\"pic.x.com/fOf4iebfED\",\n            \"media_key\":\"13_2050011774137548801\"\n          }\n        ]\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"text\":\"Un estudiante estadounidense recibió una beca de $3.000 de su universidad. Gastó cada centavo en 5 Mac Minis.\\n\\nLos numeró del 1 al 5. Los apiló en un estante. Conectó medidores de electricidad a un lado. Se preparó unos fideos instantáneos. Se fue a dormir.\\n\\nSus vecinos de la https://t.co/rbLDyKaDC2 https://t.co/riORxKd