{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8212808444\",\n  \"message_id\": \"362\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"sender\": \"B G\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-05-02 16:10 EDT\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"B G (8212808444)\",\n  \"id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"name\": \"B G\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"9547da3e","parentId":"6bb6d707","timestamp":"2026-05-02T20:11:23.875Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"fbeab54e","parentId":"9547da3e","timestamp":"2026-05-02T20:11:39.221Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby is asking what I need to know as his X agent to help him better. This is a good meta question - he's asking me to articulate what information would be useful for me to have to do my job well as his X/Twitter specialist.\n\nLet me think about what I need to know:\n\n1. **His goals for X** - What does he want to accomplish? Grow followers? Make money? Build a brand? Promote his YouTube/content?\n\n2. **His niche/topic focus** - What does he post about primarily? What does he want to be known for?\n\n3. **His target audience** - Who is he trying to reach?\n\n4. **His current following/engagement** - What's working, what's not\n\n5. **Time commitment** - How often does he want to post? Does he want me to post on his behalf or just help him create content?\n\n6. **Monetization goals** - Does he want to make money directly from X (affiliates, deals) or use it to drive traffic elsewhere?\n\n7. **Content preferences** - Video vs text vs images? Long threads vs short posts? Tone?\n\n8. **Competitors/accounts he admires** - Who does he follow and want to be like?\n\n9. **The local lead gen business** - Does he want to use X to promote his own lead gen services? Does he want me to help with that?\n\nAs his X agent, I should know things that would help me:\n- Create content he'll actually use\n- Find relevant opportunities (posts to engage with, people to follow, trends to ride)\n- Help him grow his account\n- Execute tasks on his behalf\n\nLet me give him a clear, focused answer.\n","thinkingSignature":"9b371eefba9f65c4c4853db2a14910058be3b2fc832ef118e83a917e157ef1c8"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nGood question. Here's what I need to know to actually do my job right:\n\n## What I Need To Help You\n\n**1. Your X Goals**\n- Grow followers? Make money directly? Drive traffic to your YouTube/content? Promote the lead gen business?\n- Quick wins vs long-term brand building?\n\n**2. What You're Posting About**\n- Your niche topics (AI, content creation, local lead gen, crypto, all of the above?)\n- Who you're trying to reach (creators, business owners, devs, your specific audience)\n\n**3. How You Want Me To Work**\n- Just content ideas + scheduling?\n- Post on your behalf automatically?\n- Monitor your feed and engage for you?\n- All of the above?\n\n**4. Who You Want To Be Like**\n- Any accounts you admire or want to emulate?\n- This helps me understand the style/tone you're going for\n\n**5. The Lead Gen Business**\n- Do you want to use X to land clients for the website building business?\n- Or is this separate from your X goals?\n\n**6. Current Pain Points**\n- What's not working now?\n- Are you posting but not getting traction?\n- Too time-consuming?\n- Don't know what to say?\n\n---\n\nThe more honest you are with me on this, the better I can actually help. I'm your X agent — think of me like a guy who lives on your timeline and handles everything X-related so you don't have to."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":55871,"output":651,"cacheRead":320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56842,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777752683875,"responseId":"06458d6cb68380384b7a1a311dbadddc"}}
