{"type":"message","id":"9ead56d0","parentId":"7036769a","timestamp":"2026-05-02T20:15:52.200Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby wants to first answer the X question so we can configure how I help him as his X agent, and then continue with the website/lead gen discussion. He hasn't answered yet but is signaling he will, so I should just acknowledge and wait for his answers.","thinkingSignature":"6d3f9d0bc0f9bcbc9c53b89a76a676059e76467bab78d91584d70df6fc0a6500"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nGot it. Take your time — answer whenever you're ready.\n\nOnce we knock out the X setup, we'll dive deep on the website building thing. I'll help you build out the full OpenClaw workflow — lead finder → site builder → outreach → closer — so you can see exactly what's possible and what to start with."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":56796,"output":120,"cacheRead":224,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57140,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777752948275,"responseId":"06458e747fa500c71cc053508278b23b"}}
