{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8212808444\",\n  \"message_id\": \"371\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"366\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"sender\": \"B G\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-05-02 23:32 EDT\",\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"B G (8212808444)\",\n  \"id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"name\": \"B G\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"X ⚡🕶️\",\n  \"body\": \"Good question. Here's what I need to know to actually do my job right:\\n\\nWhat I Need To Help You\\n\\n1. Your X Goals\\n\\n• Grow followers? Make money directly? Drive traffic to your YouTube/content? Promote the lead gen business?\\n• Quick wins vs long-term brand building?\\n\\n2. What You're Posting About\\n\\n• Your niche topics (AI, content creation, local lead gen, crypto, all of the above?)\\n• Who you're trying to reach (creators, business owners, devs, your specific audience)\\n\\n3. How You Want Me To Work\\n\\n• Just content ideas + scheduling?\\n• Post on your behalf automatically?\\n• Monitor your feed and engage for you?\\n• All of the above?\\n\\n4. Who You Want To Be Like\\n\\n• Any accounts you admire or want to emulate?\\n• This helps me understand the style/tone you're going for\\n\\n5. The Lead Gen Business\\n\\n• Do you want to use X to land clients for the website building business?\\n• Or is this separate from your X goals?\\n\\n6. Current Pain Points\\n\\n• What's not working now?\\n• Are you posting but not getting traction?\\n• Too time-consuming?\\n• Don't know what to say?\\n\\n───\\n\\nThe more honest you are with me on this, the better I can actually help. I'm your X agent — think of me like a guy who lives on your timeline and handles everything X-related so you don't have to.\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-