{"type":"message","id":"ad6bb14b","parentId":"35fa01ca","timestamp":"2026-05-03T03:33:53.943Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby wants me to create a simple web form with the questions I asked, host it locally, and he can fill it out and submit it to me. Let me build this as a simple HTML form that posts to a local endpoint.\n\nI can create a simple HTML file with the questions and set up a local server. Since I'm on macOS, I can use a simple Python HTTP server or Node.js to host it. Or I could just create the HTML file and give Bobby instructions on how to serve it.\n\nActually, the cleanest approach would be:\n1. Create an HTML form with all the questions\n2. Use a simple local HTTP server to serve it\n\n\n3. When Bobby submits the form, I'll have it send the data directly to me through a webhook or API endpoint that OpenClaw can listen on.\n\nActually, I think the simplest approach is just to create the HTML form locally and give Bobby a command to serve it. I'd set up an Express server or Python HTTP server that Bobby can run with one command, then point him to localhost:3000 to access the form.\n\nWait, I could make this even easier - instead of setting up a server myself, I could just save the HTML file and have Bobby open it directly in their browser. But then the form submission becomes tricky without a backend to receive it. I could use a query parameter approach or Formspree, but Formspree requires an API key. The best solution is to create a single HTML file with inline JavaScript that handles the form submission, and use Python's built-in HTTP server to host it locally - Bobby just runs one command and accesses it at localhost:8000. When the form submits, the data gets sent as a query string that I can capture and display for Bobby.\n\nThis is simple, Bobby doesn't need to install anything extra since Python is already on his Mac, and I can show him the submitted data right there on the page.","thinkingSignature":"e9f4b67a6862ae9dcbee9464052f85e6b21b2067e171dc8fee25f5c4de40590f"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n100% makes sense. Let me build that real quick.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_w449psatufxc_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>X Agent Onboarding</title>\n  <style>\n    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #0d0d0d; color: #e5e5e5; min-height: 100vh; padding: 40px 20px; }\n    .container { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }\n    h1 { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; color: #fff; }\n    .subtitle { color: #666; margin-bottom: 40px; font-size: 14px; }\n    .section { background: #1a1a1a; border: 1px solid #2a2a2a; border-radius: 16px; padding: 28px; margin-bottom: 24px; }\n    .section h2 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid #2a2a2a; padding-bottom: 12px; }\n    label { display: block; font-size: 13px; color: #888; margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 500; }\n    .question { margin-bottom: 20px; }\n    .question:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }\n    input, select, textarea { width: 100%; background: #111; border: 1px solid #333; border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px 14px; color: #fff; font-size: 15px; outline: none; transition: border-color 0.2s; }\n    input:focus, select:focus, textarea:focus { border-color: #555; }\n    textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 80px; font-family: inherit; }\n    .radio-group label, .checkbox-group label { display: inline-block; margin-right: 20px; margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 14px; color: #ccc; cursor: pointer; }\n    .radio-group input, .checkbox-group input { width: auto; margin-right: 6px; }\n    .submit-btn { width: 100%; background: #fff; color: #000; border: none; border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; transition: opacity 0.2s; }\n    .submit-btn:hover { opacity: 0.85; }\n    #submitted { display: none; background: #1a2e1a; border: 1px solid #2a4a2a; border-radius: 16px; padding: 28px; text-align: center; }\n    #submitted h2 { color: #4ade80; font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; }\n    #submitted p { color: #666; font-size: 14px; }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <h1>X Agent Onboarding</h1>\n    <p class=\"subtitle\">Fill this out so I know how to help you best. Then hit submit.</p>\n\n    <div id=\"form-wrap\">\n      <form id=\"main-form\">\n\n        <!-- SECTION 1: GOALS -->\n        <div class=\"section\">\n          <h2>1. Your X Goals</h2>\n          <div class=\"question\">\n            <label>What are you trying to get out of X? (pick what matters most)</label>\n            <div class=\"checkbox-group\">\n              <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"goals\" value=\"grow_followers\"> Grow followers</label>\n              <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"goals\" value=\"make_money_directly\"> Make money directly</label>\n              <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"goals\" value=\"drive_traffic\"> Drive traffic to YouTube/content</label>\n              <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"goals\" value=\"promote_lead_gen\"> Promote lead gen business</label>\n              <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"goals\" value=\"build_personal_brand\"> Build personal brand</label>\n              <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"goals\" value=\"network\"> Network with people in my space</label>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"question\">\n            <label>Quick wins vs long-term brand building — which are you leaning toward?</label>\n            <input type=\"text\" name=\"timeline\" placeholder=\"e.g. want results fast / playing the long game / somewhere in between\">\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- SECTION 2: WHAT YOU'RE POSTING ABOUT -->\n        <div class=\"section\">\n          <h2>2. What You're Posting About</h2>\n          <div class=\"question\">\n            <label>What topics do you post about (or want to post about)?</label>\n            <div class=\"checkbox-group\">\n              <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"topics\" value=\"ai_contentCreation\"> AI / Content Creation</label>\n              <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"topics\" value=\"local_lead_gen\"> Local Lead Gen / Website Business</label>\n              <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"topics\" value=\"crypto\"> Crypto / DeFi</label>\n              <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"topics\" value=\"music\"> Music</label>\n              <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"topics\" value=\"faceless_youtube\"> Faceless YouTube Shorts</label>\n              <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"topics\" value=\"tech\"> Tech / Tools</label>\n              <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"topics\" value=\"business\"> Business / Entrepreneurship</label>\n              <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"topics\" value=\"lifestyle\"> Lifestyle</label>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"question\">\n            <label>Who is your target audience?</label>\n            <input type=\"text\" name=\"audience\" placeholder=\"e.g. aspiring creators / local business owners / crypto degens / devs\">\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- SECTION 3: HOW YOU WANT ME TO WORK -->\n        <div class=\"section\">\n          <h2>3. How You Want Me To Work</h2>\n          <div class=\"question\">\n            <label>What do you want me doing on X? (check all that apply)</label>\n            <div class=\"checkbox-group\">\n              <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"agent_tasks\" value=\"content_ideas\"> Content ideas + scheduling</label>\n              <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"agent_tasks\" value=\"post_on_behalf\"> Post on your behalf automatically</label>\n              <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"agent_tasks\" value=\"monitor_feed\"> Monitor feed and engage for you</label>\n              <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"agent_tasks\" value=\"reply_to_dms\"> Reply to people/DMs</label>\n              <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"agent_tasks\" value=\"research_trends\"> Research trends + find content</label>\n              <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"agent_tasks\" value=\"lead_gen_outreach\"> Lead gen outreach</label>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- SECTION 4: WHO YOU WANT TO BE LIKE -->\n        <div class=\"section\">\n          <h2>4. Who You Want To Emulate</h2>\n          <div class=\"question\">\n            <label>Any accounts you admire or want to copy the style of? (handles or names)</label>\n            <textarea name=\"inspirations\" placeholder=\"e.g. @someguy - I like how he writes short punchy posts, or that tech meme guy\"></textarea>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"question\">\n            <label>What vibe do you want? (check what fits)</label>\n            <div class=\"checkbox-group\">\n              <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"vibe\" value=\"chill\"> Chill, laid back</label>\n              <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"vibe\" value=\"edgy\"> Edgy, no filter</label>\n              <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"vibe\" value=\"edu\"> Educational, informative</label>\n              <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"vibe\" value=\"meme\"> Meme-heavy, funny</label>\n              <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"vibe\" value=\"alpha\"> Alpha, drop truth bombs</label>\n              <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"vibe\" value=\"raw\"> Raw, authentic, no guru shit</label>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- SECTION 5: LEAD GEN BUSINESS -->\n        <div class=\"section\">\n          <h2>5. The Lead Gen Website Business</h2>\n          <div class=\"question\">\n            <label>Do you want to use X to land clients for the website building business?</label>\n            <div class=\"radio-group\">\n              <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"x_leadgen\" value=\"yes\"> Yes — that's the main goal</label>\n              <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"x_leadgen\" value=\"maybe\"> Maybe / still figuring it out</label>\n              <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"x_leadgen\" value=\"no\"> No — X and the business are separate</label>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"question\">\n            <label>What's your current status with the website business?</label>\n            <select name=\"business_status\">\n              <option value=\"\">— pick one —</option>\n              <option value=\"just_starting\">Just thinking about it</option>\n              <option value=\"researching\">Already researching / have a plan</option>\n              <option value=\"some_sites\">Built a few sites already</option>\n              <option value=\"already_making_money\">Already making money from it</option>\n            </select>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- SECTION 6: PAIN POINTS -->\n        <div class=\"section\">\n          <h2>6. What's Not Working</h2>\n          <div class=\"question\">\n            <label>What are your biggest pain points right now? (check all that apply)</label>\n            <div class=\"checkbox-group\">\n              <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"pain\" value=\"no_time\"> Posting takes too much time</label>\n              <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"pain\" value=\"no_ideas\"> Don't know what to post about</label>\n              <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"pain\" value=\"no_traction\"> Posting but not getting traction</label>\n              <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"pain\" value=\"burned_out\"> Burned out from creating</label>\n              <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"pain\" value=\"inconsistent\"> Inconsistent / can't stick to a schedule</label>\n              <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"pain\" value=\"not_selling\"> Posts don't lead to anything selling</label>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"question\">\n            <label>Anything else I should know about you or your goals?</label>\n            <textarea name=\"anything_else\" placeholder=\"whatever's on your mind\"></textarea>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <button type=\"submit\" class=\"submit-btn\">Submit to Agent X</button>\n      </form>\n    </div>\n\n    <div id=\"submitted\">\n      <h2>Submitted. Got it.</h2>\n      <p>I'm reading through your answers now. Give me a minute.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <script>\n    document.getElementById('main-form').addEventListener('submit', async function(e) {\n      e.preventDefault();\n      const form = e.target;\n      const data = new FormData(form);\n      const result = {};\n      for (let [key, val] of data.entries()) {\n        if (result[key]) {\n          if (Array.isArray(result[key])) result[key].push(val);\n          else result[key] = [result[key], val];\n        } else {\n          result[key] = val;\n        }\n      }\n      // Convert checkbox arrays to regular arrays\n      const checkboxes = ['goals','topics','agent_tasks','vibe','pain'];\n      checkboxes.forEach(k => { if (Array.isArray(result[k])) result[k] = result[k]; });\n      // Build readable text\n      let text = 'X AGENT ONBOARDING — BOBBY\\'S ANSWERS\\n================================\\n\\n';\n      Object.keys(result).forEach(key => {\n        text += key.replace(/_/g,' ') + ': ' + JSON.stringify(result[key]) + '\\n';\n      });\n      // Send to agent via a small fetch to a local webhook-like endpoint\n      // We'll use a simple approach: save to a temp file and notify\n      try {\n        await fetch('http://localhost:18789/submit', {\n          method: 'POST',\n          headers: {'Content-Type':'application/json'},\n          body: JSON.stringify(result)\n        });\n      } catch(err) {\n        // fallback: just show submitted\n      }\n      document.getElementById('form-wrap').style.display = 'none';\n      document.getElementById('submitted').style.display = 'block';\n    });\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n","path":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-x/onboarding-form/index.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":57065,"output":3454,"cacheRead":128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60647,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777779173375,"responseId":"0645f4e6b41a35eabb0a66da1dc7a5eb"}}
