{"type":"message","id":"2bbd926f","parentId":"a2478aa2","timestamp":"2026-05-03T03:55:01.973Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a great, comprehensive onboarding response. Let me extract the key points:\n\n1. **Goals**: Grow followers + audience, make money (long-term), drive traffic to music/apps, build personal brand, network with similar people\n2. **Timeline**: Both long-term and quick wins\n3. **Topics**: Music, apps I make, OpenClaw workflows, faceless YouTube, mix of everything I'm interested in. Not sure about lifestyle but could be interested\n4. **Target audience**: Not defined yet - just knows they want to be authentic. Blunt, funny, says what they want.\n5. **How I want to work**: \n   - Content ideas + post on his behalf ONLY after he approves\n   - Monitor feed so he can jump into conversations\n   - Learn what he's interested in/not interested in\n   - Note when interests change\n   - Help reply to DMs\n   - Every 24hrs: scroll through new likes/bookmarks to find things to work on/talk about more\n   - First need to go through ALL existing likes/bookmarks before setting up the 24hr system\n   - Clarify with him before starting the bookmark/like scanning\n6. **Inspirations**: Goes to Alex Finn's X a lot to learn about OpenClaw. Also interested in Hermes Agent but doesn't know setup/difference from OpenClaw\n7. **Vibe**: Raw and authentic\n8. **Lead gen business**: Not sure about using X for it yet\n9. **Business status**: Just an idea - hasn't started yet\n10. **Pain points**: Doesn't want to take time/brain power to come up with content, doesn't know what's trending, wants to maximize opportunities\n\nKey things to note:\n- He wants me to POST ON HIS BEHALF but only AFTER he approves\n- He wants me to monitor his feed and engage when interesting\n- He wants me to learn his interests over time\n- He wants DM notifications and help replying\n- Every 24hrs: check new likes/bookmarks + go through ALL existing ones first, then set up the 24hr system. Need to clarify with him before starting.\n\n\n- Alex Finn is someone I should keep in mind as a reference point\n- Hermes Agent could be useful to explore as another tool option\n\nI should acknowledge that I've got what I need and move forward with the workflow he described - posting content for approval, monitoring his feed for engagement opportunities, tracking his interests over time, and setting up the bookmark/like scanning system once I have his go-ahead.\n","thinkingSignature":"7046c070a6dfed9596d4fb966fbfc20af2374732e09051a5d3d1631bae90ed4a"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nGot everything I need. Let me summarize what I'm taking away:\n\n---\n\n**How I work for you:**\n\n- **Content**: I come up with ideas + write posts, you approve before anything goes live\n- **Feed monitoring**: I watch what's happening so you can jump in on convos that matter to you\n- **Learning**: I pay attention to what you like, don't like, and update continuously — no need to repeat yourself\n- **DMs**: I flag them and help you reply\n- **Likes & Bookmarks**: I go through ALL of them first (you have like 1,176 of them lol), then we set up a daily scan going forward. Will clarify with you before starting that.\n\n**Your vibe**: Raw, authentic, blunt, funny. You are who you are online and that's non-negotiable. Not changing for the algorithm.\n\n**Topics**: Music + apps you build + OpenClaw workflows + faceless YouTube — mix of everything you're actually doing.\n\n**Goal**: Make money on X somehow, either directly or by driving your audience to outside stuff (music, apps). Build a real personal brand while also getting quick wins.\n\n**Reference point**: Alex Finn — you go there for OpenClaw stuff. Also mentioned Hermes Agent as something you want to figure out.\n\n---\n\nQuick question before I set things up: **how often do you want to post?** Like every day, a few times a week, whenever something worth saying comes up? And do you want me to batch content ideas once a week or drip them as they come?\n\nOnce you answer that I'll set up the full workflow and we can start."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":62587,"output":859,"cacheRead":128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63574,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777780473103,"responseId":"0645f9f98e54e209e3f561d014662e2d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b045ded0","parentId":"2bbd926f","timestamp":"2026-05-03T03:57:10.287Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"i would like to post as frequently as neccisary to stay relevant and gain an audience on x. also, did you see my thing of what i wanted you to do every 24 hrs with my bookmarked and liked posts or did you skip over that?"}],"timestamp":1777780630285}}
