{"type":"message","id":"fddb9dad","parentId":"764b53c1","timestamp":"2026-05-03T03:59:44.434Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby said yes to going through all likes and bookmarks. Let me set up a background task to go through all likes and bookmarks, then set up the ongoing 24-hour job.\n\nI need to:\n1. Get all his likes (up to 1176+)\n2. Get all his bookmarks\n3. Build a profile of what he's into\n4. Set up a cron job for every 24 hrs to scan new ones\n\nLet me start by getting all his likes. The xurl likes command should work. Let me check how many pages there are. The X API paginates with tokens.\n\nLet me start pulling his likes. I'll need to paginate through them.\n","thinkingSignature":"68e5e8980240c22d1bb68a796b4a44b14e8dc98b535cedde1d5420044d1e7c64"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nOn it. Going through all your likes and bookmarks now.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4nu4f11pj9cf_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"xurl likes -n 100 2>&1 | head -200","timeout":20}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4nu4f11pj9cf_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"xurl bookmarks -n 100 2>&1 | head -200","timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":63083,"output":242,"cacheRead":320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63645,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777780759087,"responseId":"0645fb17d876e947ae8e4f2c65680623"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d5bb1721","parentId":"fddb9dad","timestamp":"2026-05-03T03:59:45.403Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_4nu4f11pj9cf_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"data\":[\n    {\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2050168915020361785\"\n      ],\n      \"id\":\"2050168915020361785\",\n      \"entities\":{\n        \"urls\":[\n          {\n            \"start\":277,\n            \"end\":300,\n            \"url\":\"https://t.co/CCrGHTl2Bb\",\n            \"expanded_url\":\"https://x.com/davidfigeira/status/2050168915020361785/video/1\",\n            \"display_url\":\"pic.x.com/CCrGHTl2Bb\",\n            \"media_key\":\"13_2050168897245003776\"\n          }\n        ]\n      },\n      \"public_metrics\":{\n        \"retweet_count\":89,\n        \"reply_count\":115,\n        \"like_count\":226,\n        \"quote_count\":0,\n        \"bookmark_count\":231,\n        \"impression_count\":15830\n      },\n      \"author_id\":\"1886018912996790272\",\n      \"text\":\"$52k–$130k/month offers are scaling with visuals like this\\n\\nno talking heads\\nno creators\\nno long explanations\\n\\njust ai visualizing what’s happening inside your body\\n\\ntight neck muscles\\nnerves firing and trapped\\npressure building where it shouldn’t\\n\\nyou don’t need to think\\nyou https://t.co/CCrGHTl2Bb\",\n      \"created_at\":\"2026-05-01T11:02:14.000Z\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2050376976750501900\"\n      ],\n      \"id\":\"2050376976750501900\",\n      \"entities\":{\n        \"urls\":[\n          {\n            \"start\":70,\n            \"end\":93,\n            \"url\":\"https://t.co/Q1s8JFBVur\",\n            \"expanded_url\":\"https://twitter.com/jukan05/status/2050375311813230608\",\n            \"display_url\":\"x.com/jukan05/status…\"\n          }\n        ]\n      },\n      \"public_metrics\":{\n        \"retweet_count\":9,\n        \"reply_count\":13,\n        \"l