{"type":"message","id":"52f68288","parentId":"81695f0c","timestamp":"2026-05-03T03:59:58.452Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The `-n` flag in xurl search is for number of results, but for raw API endpoints it doesn't work the same way. Let me try without -n for the raw API endpoints.\n\nActually the issue is that xurl search uses `-n` but for raw endpoints it's different. Let me try without `-n`.\n","thinkingSignature":"fb0ef68ddd5f8b7cdd226ef4e1e35e0d9c2e1576818de9d95d83bcade8fe8525"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4w215fhxsrsk_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"xurl /2/users/1959983838211260416/liked_tweets 2>&1 | head -100","timeout":15}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4w215fhxsrsk_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"xurl /2/users/1959983838211260416/bookmarks 2>&1 | head -100","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":237,"output":175,"cacheRead":65600,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66012,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777780792392,"responseId":"0645fb38b22942bd5d76cd054cc34bab"}}
{"type":"message","id":"70c32138","parentId":"52f68288","timestamp":"2026-05-03T03:59:59.017Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_4w215fhxsrsk_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"data\":[\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2050168915020361785\",\n      \"text\":\"$52k–$130k/month offers are scaling with visuals like this\\n\\nno talking heads\\nno creators\\nno long explanations\\n\\njust ai visualizing what’s happening inside your body\\n\\ntight neck muscles\\nnerves firing and trapped\\npressure building where it shouldn’t\\n\\nyou don’t need to think\\nyou https://t.co/CCrGHTl2Bb\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2050168915020361785\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2050376976750501900\",\n      \"text\":\"Buy hardware when you can afford.\\n\\nStart building your own local LLMs https://t.co/Q1s8JFBVur\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2050376976750501900\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2050289151010848783\",\n      \"text\":\"nah bro no way \\\"baddie to baddie\\\" hook is still viral.\\n\\ni posted this hook months ago.\\n\\na $40k/month skincare app is doing 500k views with this hook \\u0026amp; commenting the app name.\\n\\nthey're not writing the app name = it feels organic.\\n\\ndon't overthink. https://t.co/XTKiStV0RI\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2050289151010848783\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2050202766186807356\",\n      \"text\":\"HOLY FUCKING SHIT!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\\n\\nIT HAPPENED!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\\n\\nFIRST INTERNET MONEY!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\\n\\n!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\\n\\n!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! https://t.co/CNtUeBdPf2 https://t.co/QRroGyuUC8\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2050202766186807356\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2050151122435002672\",\n      \"text\":\"I tested Pika Agent today…\\n\\nAnd yeah it’s insane.\\n\\nTold it what I wanted, and it helped me create a full project like a real human collaborator.\\n\\nAI creation just became effortless. https://t.co/w4OUtdz1zr https://t.co/29fe20S1FY\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2050151122435002672\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2050158295911137370\",\n      \"text\":\"OpenClaw 现在可以抓取任何网站而不被屏蔽——零机器人检测，原生绕过 Cloudflare，比 BeautifulSoup 快 774 倍。\\n\\n无需维护选择器。无需变通方案。只需数据。\\n\\n这是不公平的优势，而且完全开源。\\nhttps://t.co/4r4Jg23jal https://t.co/tB8GcY7zjC\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2050158295911137370\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2050261337906016505\",\n      \"text\":\"Apple spent 7 years and $3,500 per unit building Vision Pro, this guy did something better with a webcam in his bedroom.\\n\\nAnd no, this isn't a render, it's running live on his laptop right now with a webcam pointed at his hands.\\n\\nThe webcam tracks 21 points on each of his hands https://t.co/UyXVHB8WpI https://t.co/pFJyJTseaC\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2050261337906016505\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2050011880886784235\",\n      \"text\":\"A 14 year old in America quit his weekend shifts at Domino's after he realized he could make more money during one lunch break with a laptop than an entire weekend making pizzas for $8.50 an hour.\\n\\nHe was sitting in a coffee shop googling roofing companies near his house for a https://t.co/fOf4iebfED\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2050011880886784235\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2050220109017354602\",\n      \"text\":\"Un estudiante estadounidense recibió una beca de $3.000 de su universidad. Gastó cada centavo en 5 Mac Minis.\\n\\nLos numeró del 1 al 5. Los apiló en un estante. Conectó medidores de electricidad a un lado. Se preparó unos fideos instantáneos. Se fue a dormir.\\n\\nSus vecinos de la https://t.co/rbLDyKaDC2 https://t.co/riORxKdEK6\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2050220109017354602\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2050213717762093555\",\n      \"text\":\"17 year olds are about to start printing $100k months with 2 shifts that just happened in the ecom space.\\n\\nMeta and Higgsfield both dropped official MCP connectors for Claude.\\n\\nWhat that means in plain English and how to set it up today: \\n\\nYou can now connect Claude directly to https://t.co/JkZbK0Y0Sv\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2050213717762093555\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2050297575819935934\",\n      \"text\":\"how is this free? \\n\\nthis guy created an entire clipping army inside his Telegram chat. \\n\\nPaste a YT link -\\u0026gt; AI finds clips -\\u0026gt; adds captions -\\u0026gt; schedules and posts. \\n\\nSocial media growth has never been easier. https://t.co/iwgpKxmiAn https://t.co/jl3ywjIx05\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2050297575819935934\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2050202786386563415\",\n      \"text\":\"A month ago, I set up Hermes Agent on an old M1 Macbook i found in a drawer.\\n\\nNow, a month in - I can't believe i was operating without it.\\n\\nHere's how I use it everyday: \\uD83D\\uDC47 https://t.co/S25g5A8O6F\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2050202786386563415\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2049968752360570894\",\n      \"text\":\"Codex 5.5 as orchestrator and Deepseek v4 as executor is a steal.\\n\\nI burnt 100M tokens in 36 hours on Deepseek v4. \\n\\nBeating Opus 4.6 with no sweat. https://t.co/1B8qmBaDua\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2049968752360570894\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2050179677428588600\",\n      \"text\":\"YOU CAN NOW PREDICT IF A VIDEO WILL GO VIRAL BEFORE POSTING IT USING A LOCAL MODEL\\n\\nhttps://t.co/GZwe3QFksy\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2050179677428588600\"\n      ]\n    },"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exi