s vecinos de la https://t.co/rbLDyKaDC2 https://t.co/riORxKdEK6\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2050213717762093555\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2050213717762093555\"\n      ],\n      \"text\":\"17 year olds are about to start printing $100k months with 2 shifts that just happened in the ecom space.\\n\\nMeta and Higgsfield both dropped official MCP connectors for Claude.\\n\\nWhat that means in plain English and how to set it up today: \\n\\nYou can now connect Claude directly to https://t.co/JkZbK0Y0Sv\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2050297575819935934\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2050297575819935934\"\n      ],\n      \"text\":\"how is this free? \\n\\nthis guy created an entire clipping army inside his Telegram chat. \\n\\nPaste a YT link -\\u0026gt; AI finds clips -\\u0026gt; adds captions -\\u0026gt; schedules and posts. \\n\\nSocial media growth has never been easier. https://t.co/iwgpKxmiAn https://t.co/jl3ywjIx05\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2050202786386563415\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2050202786386563415\"\n      ],\n      \"text\":\"A month ago, I set up Hermes Agent on an old M1 Macbook i found in a drawer.\\n\\nNow, a month in - I can't believe i was operating without it.\\n\\nHere's how I use it everyday: \\uD83D\\uDC47 https://t.co/S25g5A8O6F\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2049968752360570894\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2049968752360570894\"\n      ],\n      \"text\":\"Codex 5.5 as orchestrator and Deepseek v4 as executor is a steal.\\n\\nI burnt 100M tokens in 36 hours on Deepseek v4. \\n\\nBeating Opus 4.6 with no sweat. https://t.co/1B8qmBaDua\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2050179677428588600\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2050179677428588600\"\n      ],\n      \"text\":\"YOU CAN NOW PREDICT IF A VIDEO WILL GO VIRAL BEFORE POSTING IT USING A LOCAL MODEL\\n\\nhttps://t.co/GZwe3QFksy\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2049944840629072168\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2049944840629072168\"\n      ],\n      \"text\":\"the entire “grind YouTube for 3 years and build a personal brand” industry just got nuked by a 19 year old with a Discord account\\n\\n$80,000/month. no camera. no editing. no algorithm. no audience. no ads. no brands. no content. \\n\\n20+ servers. Claude-written bots. $5 Railway https://t.co/7jCCQ94e7q https://t.co/qPIXtLctQO\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2049958364654821596\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2049958364654821596\"\n      ],\n      \"text\":\"tiktok is pushing a netflix competitor where one guy posting ai cartoons about fruit is doing 43M views right now https://t.co/SLu0En6Ofs https://t.co/QXo3gjjx1b\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2049584756359115099\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2049584756359115099\"\n      ],\n      \"text\":\"14-year-old American found a roofing company on Google Maps with 4.9 stars and no website, copied their reviews and pasted them into ChatGPT 5.5.\\n\\n2 minutes later - a complete brief. \\n\\nPasted it into webuil io and just waited while the system built a full website with all pages, https://t.co/4yj1RcmVOo https://t.co/m059GRyN52\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2049560370474529217\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2049560370474529217\"\n      ],\n      \"text\":\"i should never be sharing this but f*ck it\\n\\nseedance 2.0 + claude code + tiktok is THE best combo for AI videos\\n\\ni cracked the formula for generating videos that look hyper realistic \\u0026amp; make your audience feel like \\\"holy shit this person gets me\\\"\\n\\ni'm finally sharing my FULL https://t.co/1Y9YksMZHR\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2049897707054289202\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2049897707054289202\"\n      ],\n      \"text\":\"Cancelled his $20 ChatGPT, his $200 Claude and his $30 Copilot, then built JARVIS on his MacBook that runs offline.\\n\\nWiFi off, microphone on, whisper transcribing every word locally, a local LLM responding in real time.\\n\\nA voice visualization that looks like Iron Man's actual https://t.co/4V9Zo2fmGl https://t.co/xv3ywrII48\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2049850988555587807\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2049850988555587807\"\n      ],\n      \"text\":\"Meta Tribe2 is a model that predicts your brain's response on videos\\n\\nso now you can edit videos with more clarity of how to compose them, what works and what doesn't\\n\\nand we built a free tool for you based on this model\\nyes, totally free\\n\\nsee details below https://t.co/u4XAIE9mEn https://t.co/hPnIUNUg8r\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2049938643154833486\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2049938643154833486\"\n      ],\n      \"text\":\"TikTok officially launched their short dramas app https://t.co/2le3u8aAf5\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2049988836160074022\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2049988836160074022\"\n      ],\n      \"text\":\"If you tried OpenClaw in group chats and got mixed results, you GOTTA try again. I changed how agents talk there, it IS SO GOOD NOW. https://t.co/uW9tcnynWr\\n\\nAnd if you used GPT and got subpar performance, switch to codex harness. https://t.co/9DDpY6TeAH\\n\\nEnable both and boom. https://t.co/4gIpLkRSpf\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2049619820875010461\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2049619820875010461\"\n      ],\n      \"text\":\"Every app I vibe code has the tech stack below\\n\\nEasy for beginners and free to start\\n\\nIf you've never built an app before, just paste this list into Codex or Claude Code and you'll be good to go:\\n\\nWeb framework: NextJS\\nHosting: Vercel\\nDatabase: Convex\\nAuth: Clerk\\nPayments: Stripe\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2049193467310645393\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2049193467310645393\"\n      ],\n      \"text\":\"NEW Hermes Desktop App is Insane (FREE)! https://t.co/jpfFVRCtZF\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2049477473843450067\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2049477473843450067\"\n      ],\n      \"text\":\"Higgsfield MCP now connects to Claude! \\uD83E\\uDDE9\\n\\nThe first way to generate visuals on Claude, powered by Seedance 2.0, GPT Images 2.0, Marketing Studio and Cinema Studio.\\n\\nResearch on Claude. Polish your prompts. Generate ads, videos and brand content via the Higgsfield connector. https://t.co/5C2slDuMMJ https://t.co/PzIFC3HLMN\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2049054434122956843\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2049054434122956843\"\n      ],\n      \"text\":\"Higgsfield AI starts at $8/month. Freepik Premium starts at $24/month. Krea AI starts at $49/month.\\n\\nAnd every single image and video you generate lives on their servers. Behind their content filters. Under their terms of service.\\n\\nSomeone built a free, open-source studio with https://t.co/23HwzsivLB\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2049280368327487503\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2049280368327487503\"\n      ],\n      \"text\":\"THIS 18/YO BUILT A 24/7 CLIPPING AGENT INSIDE TELEGRAM!!\\n\\nall you have to do is paste a YT link: \\n\\n- AI analyzes the entire video\\n- finds clips that will actually get views \\n- adds hooking caption styles\\n- schedules and posts on TT, IG, and YT\\n\\nVibe-marketing is finally here. https://t.co/0p2GcPM2Wb\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2049244932477759767\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2049244932477759767\"\n      ],\n      \"text\":\"Sigma: A fully private AI browser that runs agents locally on your machine.\\n\\n-No cloud.\\n\\n-No data leaving your device.\\n\\n-Open Source\\n\\nQwen, Gemma, Nemotron – all running right in your browser. This is the direction browser AI should go! https://t.co/JlTPqueuKR\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2049174934891692528\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2049174934891692528\"\n      ],\n      \"text\":\"Higgsfield MCP is HERE! \\uD83E\\uDDE9\\n\\nYou can now create content end-to-end inside any agent: OpenClaw, Hermes Agent, NemoClaw.\\n\\nThe only way to get agentic access to Seedance 2.0, GPT Images 2.0, and every other top model.\\n\\nLet your agents build content while you sleep. https://t.co/ptgIppoWLE\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2049147123652833662\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2049147123652833662\"\n      ],\n      \"text\":\"i set up this tikt0k automation 30 days ago\\n\\n\\u0026gt; posted 2x a day (58 total posts)\\n\\u0026gt; 274.7k views, 43.7k likes, 72 comments, 15.61% ER https://t.co/tzPwMFqqZz\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2049194377751437470\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2049194377751437470\"\n      ],\n\n⚠️ [... middle content omitted — showing head and tail ...]\n\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2043812722094014471\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2043806267496415576\",\n        \"2043812722094014471\"\n      ],\n      \"text\":\"Founders method using my 5.1 system\\n\\nAI UGC ads are my top performers now because of the creative freedom. \\n\\nI can spin narratives on demand with any mockup actor I want. And get an ad like this for under $10.\\n\\nFrom concept to launch in an hour… there’s nothing like it. https://t.co/9EhuMRsUCZ\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2044054827911520402\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2044054827911520402\"\n      ],\n      \"text\":\"“But Youtube Automation is too hard” https://t.co/GUyneWKXNB\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2043811213902234080\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2043811213902234080\"\n      ],\n      \"text\":\"\\u0026gt; everyone building AI chatbots\\n\\u0026gt; everyone building AI writing tools\\n\\u0026gt; everyone competing in the same crowded market\\n\\u0026gt; meanwhile 6 opportunities are sitting wide open\\n\\u0026gt; clear ROI, real demand, barely any competition\\n\\u0026gt; each one can be validated in a weekend\\n\\u0026gt; nobody's talking https://t.co/U6nXr1Nw0n https://t.co/DjyHTPtbzu\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2043960862965150011\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2043960862965150011\"\n      ],\n      \"text\":\"BABE WAKE UP.\\n\\nHermes Agent v0.9.0 just dropped.\\n\\nWhat's new:\\n\\u0026gt; Local web dashboard (manage your agent from a browser)\\n\\u0026gt; iMessage support\\n\\u0026gt; WeChat and WeCom native\\n\\u0026gt; Android via Termux\\n\\u0026gt; Fast mode for OpenAI and Anthropic\\n\\u0026gt; Pluggable context engine\\n\\u0026gt; Background process monitoring https://t.co/hRcZx9vQrO https://t.co/LBEwXj2ZlE\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2044225790032691437\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2044225790032691437\"\n      ],\n      \"text\":\"SOMEONE PUT AN OPENCLAW-RUN VENDING MACHINE IN SAN FRANCISCO\\n\\nan AI agent is running an actual physical vending machine\\n\\nOpenClaw decides what to sell, how to name the products, how to price them, creates the ads, and tracks all the sales \\n\\nyou can even see a dashboard of all the https://t.co/l62fsfuJQ2\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2044185657128649115\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2044185657128649115\"\n      ],\n      \"text\":\"Running OpenClaw alone is leaving 80% of its power on the table.\\n\\nHere's the full multi-agent setup with Hermes that changes everything:\\n\\nThe core idea:\\nStop arguing OpenClaw vs Hermes. They have different strengths. Run them as a team - one plans, one executes. One builds, one https://t.co/CyRMo5ic8n\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2043770365369876979\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2043770365369876979\"\n      ],\n      \"text\":\"Hermes Agent v0.9.0 - “The Everywhere Release”\\n\\nFull changelog below ↓ https://t.co/aG5M6owBNS\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2044142803106898382\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2044142803106898382\"\n      ],\n      \"text\":\"OpenClaw and Hermes agent are INCREDIBLE together\\n\\nIt's not about using one or the other. It's about learning how to use them as an AI agent team\\n\\nIn this video I go over the strengths and weaknesses of each, plus show you 4 workflows that will skyrocket your productivity: https://t.co/Vv5qKH0Vgl\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\":\"2043900482155098212\",\n      \"edit_history_tweet_ids\":[\n        \"2043900482155098212\"\n      ],\n      \"text\":\"Running OpenClaw on a VPS is a scam. A vast majority of people telling you to do this are getting paid by the VPS companies\\n\\nThey're not even running OpenClaw on a VPS themselves\\n\\nWhy do you need a Mac Mini for OpenClaw? Simple:\\n\\n• MacOS is insanely easy to set up and use\\n• You https://t.co/380HU2L2A9\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"meta\":{\n    \"result_count\":100,\n    \"next_token\":\"7140dibdnow9c7btw4b2e9hxwln982bbb3l7h2ofl7lf7\"\n  }\n}[... 21876 more characters truncated]"}],"details":{"persistedDetailsTruncated":true,"originalDetailsBytesAtLeast":8193,"originalDetailKeys":["status","exitCode","durationMs","aggregated","cwd"],"status":"completed","cwd":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-x","exitCode":0},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777780801792}}
