{"type":"message","id":"fb08198d","parentId":"53ccddac","timestamp":"2026-05-03T04:06:40.507Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me write up a clean summary for Bobby. This is a lot of useful info.\n","thinkingSignature":"b87ff16a6e08e69a788539ae55904accac772752de191ed218703b41c3cb4f4a"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nDone. Here's what I found:\n\n---\n\n## Your Likes Summary — 1,132 posts analyzed\n\n**Top things you're into (by likes):**\n\n| Topic | Count |\n|---|---|\n| OpenClaw workflows & setups | 176 |\n| AI video / clipping tools | 157 |\n| Telegram automation bots | 157 |\n| YouTube automation | 102 |\n| Content growth on X | 59 |\n| Money making with AI | 59 |\n| Local lead gen / website business | 43 |\n| Mac Mini / local AI setups | 28 |\n| Hermes Agent | 24 |\n| Music + AI | 7 |\n\n**Top accounts you engage with:**\n- @openclaw (the most — 27 times)\n- @moltbook, @MiniMax_AI, @steipete, @v_computer\n- @ashen_one, @Polymarket, @grok, @DanScavino\n\n**Things I noticed:**\n- You're heavy into AI agent content — OpenClaw dominates your feed\n- You have a real interest in the local lead gen / website business thing (43 likes)\n- YouTube automation is big for you (102 likes)\n- Very interested in AI video / clipping (157 likes)\n- You interact with a lot of growth / money-making alpha accounts\n- Not much music content yet — but you have music you want to push\n- You engage with Polymarket and crypto stuff but it's not dominant\n\n---\n\n## How I'll Use This\n\nGoing forward, every 24hrs I'll:\n1. Check your new likes since last check (using the checkpoint)\n2. Flag anything we can build on, talk about, or use for content\n3. If no new ones, tell you \"no new likes since last check\"\n\n**Already set up:** Last like ID stored, script ready to run daily.\n\n---\n\nNow — want to move into the website building thing or do you want me to come up with some content ideas first based on what I just found?"}],"api":"anthropic