{"type":"message","id":"4975e0f6","parentId":"62e35f35","timestamp":"2026-05-03T04:07:27.405Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby wants me to:\n1. When processing X posts with videos, download the video\n2. Transcribe it\n3. Save the transcript and summary + the link in a file\n4. Delete the video after to save storage\n5. This gives more context on posts with videos\n\nLet me update the analyze-likes script and the ongoing monitoring script to include this capability. I'll need to use the video-frames skill or whisper for transcription.\n\nLet me check if there's a transcription tool available - I saw the openai-whisper skill earlier. Let me read that skill file to understand how to use it.\n","thinkingSignature":"85d4dea84ced4e6418629092b4be4b59ce3c4cbae5b77b63a551e94d8a0acded"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4nohb6egsuci_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/openai-whisper/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":75231,"output":169,"cacheRead":192,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75592,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777781232109,"responseId":"0645fcf50d784fd6cc7f339bf0dc0db5"}}
{"type":"message","id":"46108d9a","parentId":"4975e0f6","timestamp":"2026-05-03T04:07:33.993Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_4nohb6egsuci_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: openai-whisper\ndescription: Local speech-to-text with the Whisper CLI (no API key).\nhomepage: https://openai.com/research/whisper\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\":\n      {\n        \"emoji\": \"🎤\",\n        \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"whisper\"] },\n        \"install\":\n          [\n            {\n              \"id\": \"brew\",\n              \"kind\": \"brew\",\n              \"formula\": \"openai-whisper\",\n              \"bins\": [\"whisper\"],\n              \"label\": \"Install OpenAI Whisper (brew)\",\n            },\n          ],\n      },\n  }\n---\n\n# Whisper (CLI)\n\nUse `whisper` to transcribe audio locally.\n\nQuick start\n\n- `whisper /path/audio.mp3 --model medium --output_format txt --output_dir .`\n- `whisper /path/audio.m4a --task translate --output_format srt`\n\nNotes\n\n- Models download to `~/.cache/whisper` on first run.\n- `--model` defaults to `turbo` on this install.\n- Use smaller models for speed, larger for accuracy.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777781253993}}
{"type":"message","id":"fb0f6b44","parentId":"46108d9a","timestamp":"2026-05-03T04:07:46.614Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Whisper is available. Now I need to update the analyze-likes script to handle videos. The process would be:\n\n1. When analyzing a like that contains a video, download the video\n2. Transcribe it using whisper\n3. Save the transcript + summary to a file\n4. Delete the video\n5. Store the link, transcript, and summary\n\nLet me update the script to handle this. I need to figure out how to download X videos. I can use yt-dlp or maybe just curl. Let me check what's available.\n\nActually, let me write a comprehensive script that:\n1. Scans likes for posts with videos\n2. Downloads the video (from the URL)\n\n\n3. Transcribes it with whisper\n4. Saves the transcript and summary to files\n5. Cleans up the video after processing\n\nI'll need to extract video URLs from the tweet data and use a download tool like yt-dlp or gallery-dl. Let me update the analysis script to handle this workflow properly.\n","thinkingSignature":"702ac015b5cd9c4a77e2ed9c0ed89144e4c4f05eb4f31b74175a9e9e5888ac14"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ie7auqjjxqkb_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"which yt-dlp 2>/dev/null || which gallery-dl 2>/dev/null || which ytdl 2>/dev/null || echo \"none found\"","timeout":5}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ie7auqjjxqkb_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"which whisper && whisper --version 2>/dev/null","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":392,"output":314,"cacheRead":75328,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76034,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777781253997,"responseId":"0645fd080c28f18df4e7e2b05eaffa83"}}
