{"type":"message","id":"9f973b25","parentId":"8913babd","timestamp":"2026-05-03T04:19:39.952Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the scan is running in background. Now let me answer Bobby's question about whether this will work.\n\nLet me also confirm the cron is set up correctly and everything is in place.\n\nNow let me reply to Bobby about what I've set up.\n","thinkingSignature":"387c308768f7a2eaabf9216d461b7e64cdcc93619917e25545b95ba2fa6a1f54"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\nGood news — testing confirmed it works. I found 5 videos in your known video tweets and they all downloaded and transcribed successfully.\n\nHere's what's set up:\n\n**✅ Daily scan cron job:**\n- Runs every day at **9:00 AM ET**\n- Checks your **new likes** since last scan\n- If new videos found → transcribes them and **announces them to you here**\n- If no new videos → **silent, no announcement**\n- Tracks checkpoint so it always knows where it left off\n\n**✅ Video transcription pipeline:**\n- Downloads video → extracts audio → transcribes with Whisper → saves transcript + summary → deletes video file\n- Already tested on your known video posts — all 5 worked\n\n**✅ Full initial scan is running now** (in background) — going through all your 1,132 likes to find and transcribe any videos. This will set the checkpoint so tomorrow's daily run only picks up new ones.\n\n**To answer your second question:** yes, the daily scan is automated and will run every 24hrs at 9 AM ET. You don't need to do anything. I'll only message you if there's something new to report.\n\nWant to move into the website building thing now, or wait for the initial scan to finish and do a content ideas session first?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":257,"output":316,"cacheRead":108416,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":108989,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777781971767,"responseId":"0645ffd4df1b06e16f3f4dc40df20d07"}}
