{"type":"message","id":"6401be50","parentId":"95e22642","timestamp":"2026-05-03T05:08:54.425Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is an OAuth2 token format used by X API - it's not a JWT, it's a special token format. The format seems to be `client_id:timestamp:version:grant_type:token_type:token_value`. The issue is that OAuth2 tokens for the X API are typically short-lived and may need to be refreshed.\n\nThe access token is `cHlqQnlEVnlCWFlIOEE5d2EzTkFfVjY2cWsyY0VxQUc5cXMyWEtCUkFXYU9sOjE3Nzc2OTE3MTg0MjM6MTowOmF0OjE` which decodes to `pyjByDVyBXYH8A9wa3NA_V66qk2cEqAG9qs2XKBRAWaOl:1777691718423:1:0:at:1`. This is a special X API token format.\n\n\nThe 401 error suggests the token itself is invalid or expired, rather than a scope issue. The error message doesn't indicate a scope problem - it says \"Unauthorized\" outright. The refresh token from the config doesn't look like a standard OAuth2 format either, which makes me wonder if the token in the config is just malformed.\n\nLet me reconsider the approach here. The browser-based method might be the most straightforward workaround if the API isn't cooperating with the credentials I have.\n","thinkingSignature":"982bbb87e09855a0fd081a77ad92714927d6b0b06d8fdf0e64b9ba735a3a71b7"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nThe OAuth2 token might be expired or invalid format. The X API OAuth2 tokens are short-lived and need to be refreshed. Rather than keep fighting the API auth, let me take the simpler browser approach — it's actually more reliable for this.\n\nHere's the plan for bookmarks:\n\nEvery 24hrs when the scan runs, I'll use the browser to go to your bookmarks page, scroll through, and collect what you have. It's slower but guaranteed to work.\n\nWant me to set that up now, or do you want to try getting fresh OAuth2 credentials first? If you want to try OAuth2 again, I'd need you to:\n\n1. Go to https://developer.x.com\n2. Navigate to your app\n3. Generate a fresh OAuth2 access token with **bookmark** scope\n4. Send me the new token\n\nOr we just go browser route and save time. Your call."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":311,"output":468,"cacheRead":113856,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114635,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777784919296,"responseId":"06460b57d2874fb296f00c391c05a734"}}
