{"type":"message","id":"339ec9e8","parentId":"7386291b","timestamp":"2026-05-03T05:15:33.421Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby wants to know what I learned from going through his likes. Let me give him a comprehensive summary of what I found from the 1,132 likes analysis I did earlier.\n","thinkingSignature":"30a830cfa4fdabb634521da6bf21c9371ccc48637d0955b18e67b678dbbaa89c"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nHere's what I learned from your 1,132 likes:\n\n**You're deep into AI agents** — OpenClaw content dominates your feed. You're not just lurking, you're paying attention to people building real workflows with it.\n\n**Your content pillars (by engagement):**\n\n**1. AI Video / Clipping Tools (157 posts)**\n- You're obsessed with AI-generated video, clipping workflows, Telegram bots that automate content posting\n- The \"clipping army in Telegram\" post you liked is right in your wheelhouse — that's faceless YouTube automation territory\n- TikTok AI content is big for you\n\n**2. OpenClaw Workflows (176 posts)**\n- You follow people doing advanced multi-agent setups\n- Hermes Agent integration is something you want to figure out\n- You're interested in the \"vibe marketing\" angle too\n\n**3. YouTube Automation (102 posts)**\n- 19 year olds making $80k/month with Discord bots\n- AI UGC ads, faceless channels\n- This connects to your music and app goals\n\n**4. Money Making / Growth Alpha (59 posts)**\n- You like posts about people making real money with AI\n- The 14 year old roofing website story (which had a video you liked) is exactly the website business model\n- Crypto and prediction markets show up occasionally\n\n**5. Local Lead Gen / Website Business (43 posts)**\n- You liked the \"14 year old using Claude to build a website for a roofer\" post\n- You've seen the Rank & Rent model discussed\n- This is where the website building thing comes in\n\n**6. Music + AI (7 posts)**\n- Not much here yet, but you have music you want to sell\n- There's room to tie this into AI-generated music content\n\n**Things you haven't touched much:**\n- Lifestyle content\n- Political stuff (beyond your general feed)\n- Anything personal / vlog-style\n\n**What this tells me about content you could make:**\n- OpenClaw workflow breakdowns (you're qualified to speak on this)\n- \"I tried this AI tool for X\" style posts\n- Faceless YouTube journey posts\n- Music + AI crossovers\n- The website building business journey\n\n**Your vibe is raw, authentic, no guru shit** — and your likes reflect that. You're following builders and hackers, not motivational speakers.\n\nWhat do you want to dig into first — website building or content ideas?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":114277,"output":539,"cacheRead":352,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115168,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777785308064,"responseId":"06460cdd6105ccd7c1c36a5a48941e2b"}}
